commentPostTextItems.html: That's it Pakistan win by 4 wickets and win the series 2-0. Razzaq and Akmal finishes it for Pakistan, good knocks from Shoaib Malik and Imran Farhat in the beginning and a wonderful 53 from Yousuf. Muralitharan bowled well for his 3 wickets. Afridi gets the Man of the match award for his 3 wickets. Abdul Razzaq is the Man of the series.

Thanks for being with us. This is your commentator Binoy George signing off. Please join us for the live coverage of the first test beginning on the 26th of March. Until then it is bye from all of us here.
